{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "29fdce16",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "# title: Marimo-quarto\n",
    "toc: false\n",
    "format:\n",
    "  html:\n",
    "    page-layout: full\n",
    "jupyter: jax-env-kernel\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "## Hypothèses communes \n",
    "\n",
    "* Le point d'indice vaut $4.92278$\n",
    "* Le SMIC est à 1867 euros bruts\n",
    "* L'indemnité de résidence vaut\n",
    "    * 3% à Palaiseau\n",
    "    * 1% à Brest\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "35220adf",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#| code-fold: true\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "valeur_point_default = 4.92278 \n",
    "SMIC = 1867\n",
    "\n",
    "res_Brest = 1.01\n",
    "res_palaiseau = 1.03\n",
    "valeur_point = valeur_point_default"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "1eef6d78",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Calcul de l'ancienneté\n",
    "On considère un recrutement après 2 années de postdoc\n",
    "\n",
    "Dans la LPR, \n",
    "* les années de thèse comptent pour 3 ans (36 mois),\n",
    "* le docotat ajoute une année de bonification (12 mois)\n",
    "* et chaque année de postdoc compte (ici 24 mois).\n",
    "\n",
    "L'ancienneté est donc de 72 mois. \n",
    "\n",
    "Dans le MESR [source](https://www.emploi-collectivites.fr/grille-indiciaire-etat-maitre-conferences/1/5141.htm), \n",
    "* Échelon 1 dure 12 mois\n",
    "* Échelon 2 dure 34 mois\n",
    "* Échelon 3 dure 34 mois\n",
    "* Échelon 4 dure 34 mois\n",
    "* Échelon 5 dure 34 mois\n",
    "\n",
    "Après deux ans de post doc on rentre donc avec 26 mois d'ancienneté dans l'échelon 3, dans lequel il reste 8 mois à faire. \n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "de51ae07",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#| code-fold: true\n",
    "\n",
    "years_mcf_default = np.array([0, 8, 12-8, 34, 34, 42, 34, 34])/12"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a227dd3f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## RIPEC\n",
    "\n",
    "La RIPEC C1 doit atteindre 6400 euros en 2027 ([source](https://www.enseignementsup-recherche.gouv.fr/fr/bo/23/Hebdo6/ESRH2302327X.htm)). Avec les retards de vote de budget, la RIPEC d'une année N peut être effective en juillet de cette année avec effet retroactif comme cela a eu lieu en 2025 ([source](https://www.sgen-cfdt.fr/actu/revalorisation-du-ripec-c1-enfin/)). On peut donc choisir avance de compter la RIPEC 2026 pour l'année en cours ou choisir de ne compter pour 2026 que la RIPEC 2025. \n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "98bd6c7f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#| code-fold: true\n",
    "\n",
    "RIPEC_2027 = 6400\n",
    "RIPEC_2026 = (6400+4800)/2\n",
    "RIPEC_2025 = 4800\n",
    "  \n",
    "indice_majore_mcf = np.array([589, 648,648, 698, 744, 774, 808, 835])\n",
    "\n",
    "RIPEC_2026_2027 = np.array([RIPEC_2026]*2 + [RIPEC_2027] * 6)/12  \n",
    "RIPEC_2025_2027 = np.array([RIPEC_2025]*2 + [RIPEC_2027] * 6)/12  \n",
    "RIPEC_2025 = np.array([RIPEC_2025] * 8)/12  \n",
    "\n",
    "RIPEC_ENSTA = 2800/12"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ef836c76",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Calcul\n",
    "\n",
    "Pour l'ENSTA\n",
    "* On part de l'IM 678\n",
    "* RIPEC C1 = 2800 euros (2026)\n",
    "* 40 points d'augmentation tous les 3 ans\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "44d960ee",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#| code-fold: true\n",
    "\n",
    "nombre_annees = 55\n",
    "augmentation_tri = 40"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "c3830a63",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#| code-fold: true\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "number_years = int(np.floor(nombre_annees/3))\n",
    "jump_indice = augmentation_tri\n",
    "start_indice_default = 678\n",
    "\n",
    "indice_majore_ENSTA_default = np.repeat(\n",
    "    [start_indice_default + i * jump_indice for i in range(number_years)],\n",
    "    3\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "years_ENSTA = np.array([0] + [1] * int(number_years-1))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "Salaire_mcf_Pal = indice_majore_mcf * valeur_point * res_palaiseau\n",
    "Salaire_mcf_Brest = indice_majore_mcf * valeur_point * res_Brest\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2025\n",
    "Salaire_mcf_Pal_2025 = Salaire_mcf_Pal + RIPEC_2025 \n",
    "Salaire_mcf_Brest_2025 = Salaire_mcf_Brest + RIPEC_2025\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2025 2027\n",
    "Salaire_mcf_Pal_2025_2027 = Salaire_mcf_Pal + RIPEC_2025_2027\n",
    "Salaire_mcf_Brest_2025_2027 = Salaire_mcf_Brest + RIPEC_2025_2027\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2026 2027\n",
    "Salaire_mcf_Pal_2026_2027 = Salaire_mcf_Pal + RIPEC_2026_2027\n",
    "Salaire_mcf_Brest_2026_2027 = Salaire_mcf_Brest + RIPEC_2026_2027\n",
    "\n",
    "### ENSTA\n",
    "Salaire_ENSTA_Pal = indice_majore_ENSTA_default * valeur_point * res_palaiseau\n",
    "Salaire_ENSTA_Brest = indice_majore_ENSTA_default * valeur_point * res_Brest\n",
    "\n",
    "Salaire_ENSTA_Pal_prime = Salaire_ENSTA_Pal + RIPEC_ENSTA\n",
    "Salaire_ENSTA_Brest_prime = Salaire_ENSTA_Brest + RIPEC_ENSTA\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "4f5833d0",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
